responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "D205660F4B0C751B67BA2593270197CE", "Awooo. Pleasant evening for a nighttime stroll, innit? I almost mistook you for a sleepwalker. Been seeing quite a few citizens wandering through here in their night clothes. Would rather avoid it myself, since it\'s a nasty habit. Bet they think they\'re still on their feather beds. Meanwhile they\'re out here with me, bracing against the chilly winds blowing through the Baneswood.")
